snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator SpongeBob SquarePants Special Pack Tease
snippet.description:
How did Bikini Bottom get so mucky?! The SpongeBob SquarePants Special Pack arrives in PowerWash Simulator this Summer on Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, Xbox Series S/X, PC and PlayStation 4 + 5!
